blank\">https://youtu.be/VBu551WLnss</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n有個日本仔做咗5分鐘定格動畫，但冇乜views ,內容係話個日本仔用少少玩嘅心態嚟香港睇示威  點知俾人鳩拉咗。佢好有心都有詳細講香港示威背景， 都幾cute, 12月29日upload上youtube, 但竟然得<strong>37views</strong>！<br />\n依家升到300.<br />\n<br />\n忍唔住要做tweet <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2uKPky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2uKPky.jpg&h=db3953e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36CC5h2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36CC5h2&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=e84642f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36CC5h2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>RT pls</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n佢有twitter不過未見有提段片，大家都可去感謝佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kakerun_shoten\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkakerun_shoten&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=3eaaf4d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/kakerun_shoten</a>"}]}